{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_2000-06-20",
 "title": "Vek's First Fighter",
 "summary": "In the auxiliary bay of the NRSC Deliverance, Colonel Altair Quila grounds the eager green cadet Vek Eldar from solo flight until his injured hand heals, permitting only sim work and escorted flights. Bazil McKenzie arrives in his new Dawntreader and looks on as Altair assigns Vek his first X-wing, Ghost 11, prompting the cadet to gush over the snubfighter like a kid with a new toy. The Quarren technician Kelvis Aquatica arrives and good-naturedly chides Altair for once again breaking parts on Ghost One while \"exploring,\" urging her to simply ask the techs for lessons. Talk turns to the doctor Jasmine being confined to quarters on the warpath, stirring veiled tension in Vek, while Bazil nurses his secret crush on Altair under the cadet's teasing scrutiny and Commander Wedge passes through to fetch Rogue Squadron status reports before Bazil departs for errands on Coruscant.",
